Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 009—\NTorn resignation letters{NOTE:破られた退部届}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Midori-san.{NOTE:みどりさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At last it's time for our turn.{NOTE:いよいよあたしたちの出番が来たようね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn?{NOTE:出番？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{NOTE:どう言う意味？}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to repay you for the last time.{NOTE:それはこの前のを返しをさせてもらうことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the act.{NOTE:強がりを止しなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The results won't change.{NOTE:いくらやっても、同じこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you've spent your spring break on some special training?{NOTE:二人共さ、休みの間にあたしたちXXなったって言うの？え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As if, hahaha.{NOTE:まさか。ヘヘヘ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.{NOTE:その通りよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, April Fools is long over.{NOTE:ね、エープリルフールは過ぎたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to make it clear: we've already proved our skill before.{NOTE:言っとくけどさ、この前実力で勝ったんですからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:お分かり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we want to repay you with skill.{NOTE:だから実力XXX返しようと言うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let you keep that boastful attitude forever. Got it?{NOTE:あなたたちにね…何時までも大きな顔させないてこと。分かる？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it.{NOTE:よく分かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the last time wasn't enough for you after all.{NOTE:どうやら、もう一度可愛がるほか成せそうだわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. Our Big Four is\htoo\hgood to accept such a request.{NOTE:馬鹿馬鹿しいじゃん。四天王XXXこんな(XXX・練習試合)にするなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No trash talk. We'll play with them all right.{NOTE:だからさ。ぐうの音もでないようにしてやるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll play with the same people.{NOTE:ファイト同じメンバーでいいのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your game.{NOTE:さ、いらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy?{NOTE:良いわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's do this.\N– What's with her.{NOTE:—やろう。\\N—なによ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.{NOTE:畜生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really doing this?{NOTE:やるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's professor Hongou.{NOTE:あ。本郷先生だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!{NOTE:先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,– Professor!\N– Professor!{NOTE:—先生！\\N—先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, did you come to be Fujimi students' good charm?{NOTE:先生、富士見の生徒XXXために来たんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taken place of our professor Kajioka as the new coach to promote yourself, no?{NOTE:あたしたちの梶岡先生下ろして、コーチに売り込んだ。そういうつもりなんでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{NOTE:なに言ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou is not like that.{NOTE:そんな本郷先生じゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did he push to become our coach?{NOTE:じゃ、なぜ無理にコーチに成ろうとしたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san.{NOTE:泉さん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Shut up.{NOTE:フン！黙って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's with Izumi-san.{NOTE:泉さん、どうしたんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's acting strange.{NOTE:何かが変よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive it.{NOTE:許せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As the club members, for you to cast us out…{NOTE:バレー部員としてあたしたちを除け者にしようなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do?{NOTE:どう言うことなのよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!{NOTE:先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you say something?{NOTE:何とか言ったらどうなんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Professor Hongou.{NOTE:そうよ。本郷先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She's yelling so much.{NOTE:こんな人怒鳴りつけて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You two stay out of this!{NOTE:XXX・思い出したと驚かないわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What it'll be, professor!{NOTE:ちょっと、先生！}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your way of talking.{NOTE:何だ、その言い方は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Students these days have no respect at all.{NOTE:生徒は先生に大して聞く口じゃないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.{NOTE:だが、ま良い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want, but you're no better doing as you please.{NOTE:こんなことと言っても、君達は勝手に今日XXだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will say just this.{NOTE:俺に言えるはただ一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In volleyball, the skill is the most important.{NOTE:バレー部はバレーの実力は第一だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I believe you said you want a grudge match.{NOTE:所で、その実力でお返しすると言っただようだが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We did.{NOTE:言いました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,– Chief…\N– We're no good.{NOTE:—親分…\\N—だって、あたしじゃん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting.{NOTE:面白いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you girls.{NOTE:それじゃ、あんたたち…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see your skills before your beloved professor Hongou.{NOTE:本郷先生の前でゆっくりとその実力を見せてもらいましょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?{NOTE:どうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.{NOTE:まあまあことないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher nailed it. We'll just kick their butts.{NOTE:先生が言ったんだもん。勝ってんかってにやっつけちゃうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.{NOTE:早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.{NOTE:ま。やろうやろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.28,Alternative,,0,0,0,,"Repay with skill". I'll believe those words.{NOTE:実力でお返しすると言った、君達の言葉を信じよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.08,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Ayuhara.{NOTE:頼むぞ、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, take your time.{NOTE:鮎原さん、一歩一歩一本。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,– Do your best!\N– Captain!{NOTE:—頑張ってね！\\N—キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ah!\N– Oh!{NOTE:—あ！\\N—お！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.52,Alternative,,0,0,0,,The curve ball.{NOTE:変化球。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.46,Alternative,,0,0,0,,"Leaf Fall".{NOTE:「木の葉落とし」。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.{NOTE:フフン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fufufu.{NOTE:へへへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you spacing out?{NOTE:何よぼやぼやしてるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a point for us.{NOTE:ポイントよ、得点。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We scored one point.{NOTE:得点をXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes ma'am! Right away.{NOTE:はーはい、ただいま。}
