Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!{NOTE:痛い…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand got numb again.{NOTE:又手が痺れた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?{NOTE:どうしよう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Izumi-san!{NOTE:あ、泉さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, captain! Nice, nice!{NOTE:わい、キャプテン！いいぞ、いいぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, maybe we should go easy on them?{NOTE:鮎原さん、すこしXXXやったら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, good going, good going!{NOTE:わい、(XXX・いいね、ふたり、いいね)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!{NOTE:わあい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:えい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho?{NOTE:ほ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides Ayuhara, Hayakawa can serve that curve ball too.{NOTE:鮎原所か、早川であの変化球サーブを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:50.56,Alternative,,0,0,0,,If you thought I'd lose to Ayuhara-san, big mistake.{NOTE:鮎原さんだけの変化球と思った、間違いよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:51.63,Alternative,,0,0,0,,How do you like it?{NOTE:いかが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san, awesome!{NOTE:早川さん、すごい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.{NOTE:信じられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.92,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It feels so strange when we're leading this easily.{NOTE:こんなに調子良く決まるなんて不思議なくらいだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.75,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the camp would be this effective.{NOTE:合宿XXこんなに覿面だなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.07,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But looks like our surprise can't compare with theirs.{NOTE:でも、あたしたち以上面食らってるのはあそこにいるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose.{NOTE:負けたくない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:13.19,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I can't lose.{NOTE:負けられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.50,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Never.{NOTE:絶対に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.67,Alternative,,0,0,0,,No way we'll lose!…{NOTE:負けるもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.33,Alternative,,0,0,0,,No way we'll lose!{NOTE:負けるもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.01,Alternative,,0,0,0,,No way we'll lose!!{NOTE:負けるもんか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.78,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Izumi became unreasonable and lost her rhythm.{NOTE:泉は無理になって、調子を崩している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:—はい。\\N—それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaa!{NOTE:あぁぁ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We won this set!{NOTE:はい、セットいただきよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, you did well!{NOTE:わい、YYY皆YYY！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it hurts…{NOTE:あ、痛い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, that was terrific.{NOTE:親分、すごい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you served with your left hand…{NOTE:左手あんなに打てるなんてさ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And that strength. That spike could dent the court.{NOTE:それも強烈！コートは(XXX・凹みそうな)スパイクね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you like current Ayuhara-san's skills?{NOTE:どう？今の鮎原さんの実力よ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…{NOTE:ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost.{NOTE:負けたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying? The match starts now.{NOTE:どうーどうして？未だ勝負がこれからよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous to decide it with a single set.{NOTE:ワンセット終わったばかりじゃない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay strong, Izumi-san.{NOTE:弱き出さないで、泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ah, Izumi-san.\N– Izumi-san.{NOTE:—あ、泉さん…\\N—泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-kun!{NOTE:泉くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Izumi?{NOTE:どうしたんだ、泉？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.47,Alternative,,0,0,0,,It's no use.{NOTE:もう駄目よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.37,Alternative,,0,0,0,,This hand just won't react.{NOTE:この手が言うこと聞かないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,– Izumi-san!\N– Izumi-san!{NOTE:—泉さん！\\N—泉さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,– Izumi-san.\N– Izumi-san, hey.{NOTE:—泉さん。\\N—泉さんたら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san.{NOTE:泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we give up midway? That's not like you, Izumi-san.{NOTE:なぜ途中でXXX？泉さんらしくないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more sets wouldn't change the outcome.{NOTE:何セットやっても、同じことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,– Eh?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?{NOTE:そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.{NOTE:そんなバカな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't argue with me. I know what I'm talking about.{NOTE:あたしには分かってるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regrettable. I'll be going home first.{NOTE:悔しいけど、先に帰るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm…{NOTE:ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was crazy.{NOTE:どうかしてるんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's so unlike Izumi-san.{NOTE:あ、泉さんらしくないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was university training camp.{NOTE:大学の合宿に参加したのか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains it.{NOTE:道理で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must've been tough, no?{NOTE:しかし、辛かったろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won with the Big Four.{NOTE:でも、四天王に勝ったですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel refreshed.{NOTE:すかっとしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, you were like Superman.{NOTE:親分てんでススーパーマンだったわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san's curve ball was awesome, too.{NOTE:早川さんだって、あんな変化球出すなんて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was super cool!{NOTE:本当、格好良かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It finally feels like volleyball club again.{NOTE:これでやっとあたしたちのバレー部らしく成った}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't want to hear their boasting ever again.{NOTE:そうよ。二度とあんなやつに口じゃさせないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't see past the end of their noses.{NOTE:天狗の鼻を折られて、ぺっちゃんこ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end they had to bump into a wall.{NOTE:ざまあご覧、遊ばせって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Heheheh.{NOTE:ヘヘヘ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah.{NOTE:ああ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Four is over.{NOTE:お終いだわ、四天王もう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Ayuhara.{NOTE:だが、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do now?{NOTE:これから一体どうするつもりだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to fix your relationship with them?{NOTE:四天王…このまま仲間外れにしておくのうかない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With the exception of Ayuhara's group, when compared to other members, they are stronger.{NOTE:鮎原達ともかく、他のメンバーと比べたら彼女達の方がはるかに実力は上だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand that too.{NOTE:それは君達を認めるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But professor.{NOTE:だって、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile for us to try joining forces with such uncooperative people.{NOTE:あんな非協力的な人たちとチーム組むなんてあたしたちはできないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.{NOTE:ヘヘヘ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Futile or not, I'm entrusting it to you.{NOTE:できるかできんかは、それはま、君達に任せよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God it? Ayuhara. Hayakawa.{NOTE:良いな？鮎原。早川。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Katori-san, what will it be?{NOTE:ね？香取さん、どうするのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel this way, it can't be helped.{NOTE:あなたたちがその気なら、しょうがないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided then.{NOTE:じゃ、決まった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After telling Izumi-san, let's put our resignation together tomorrow.{NOTE:泉さんに話して、明日は四人一緒に退部届けよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.{NOTE:了解。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd want to be in that club anyway.{NOTE:誰があんなバレー部いてやるもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it straight!{NOTE:(XXX・黄線)だ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, fight!{NOTE:ファイト、ファイト！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't space out!{NOTE:ぼやぼやするな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the ball closely!{NOTE:良く玉を見ろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what professor said…{NOTE:先生あんなこと言うけど、}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.{NOTE:無理よね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?{NOTE:無理って？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Four are sure to quit the club now.{NOTE:四天王きっと止めちゃうわ、バレー部を。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them do that.{NOTE:やめさせるわけにはいかないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Our power will fall considerably.{NOTE:あたしたち先じゃ大変な戦力低下よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weak, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:弱気な、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without the Big Four we're plenty capable on our own.{NOTE:四天王なんかいなくだって、あたしたちって十分やっていけるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I wonder about that.{NOTE:あ、それはどうかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumi-san acted strange today.{NOTE:今の泉さん何とか変だもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she gave it all she had.{NOTE:あれは実力と思えないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll try talking to them tomorrow again.{NOTE:とにかく、明日もう一度話してみるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.{NOTE:無駄よ、無駄。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive they'll drop out.{NOTE:退部直ぐに決まってます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely won't let them do that.{NOTE:んん。絶対に退部させないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,– You're so stubborn.\N– Same goes to you.{NOTE:—強情ね。\\N—あなたこそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be a realist.{NOTE:いいや、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you, captain.{NOTE:キャプテンにお任せするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.55,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll take my chances.{NOTE:やってみる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.35,Alternative,,0,0,0,,I'll show you that I can persuade the Big Four.{NOTE:あたしの力で四天王を説得してみせる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H141414&\3c&H141414&\t(0,1500,\1c&H9AFBDC&\3c&H202020&)}Club resignation letter{NOTE:退部届}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, now that we have our letters ready…{NOTE:さ、それで三人の退部届は揃ったわけない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Izumi-san?{NOTE:ね、泉さんは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's absent today.{NOTE:それはさ、お休みらしいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd deliver the letters with all four of us.{NOTE:どうせ、退部届らすなら四人に一緒にと思ったのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened to Izumi-san.{NOTE:一体どうしたかしら、泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterdays game must've gotten to her.{NOTE:昨日のショックは大きいなのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely.{NOTE:きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,Izumi family{NOTE:泉}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,By "no" I mean "no".{NOTE:いやったら、いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go to the hospital again.{NOTE:大の病院なんかいつもんですか、絶対いや。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks very painful.{NOTE:だって、とても痛そうじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing more with that arm is reckless.{NOTE:その腕で試合をするなんて無茶ですよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?{NOTE:ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.{NOTE:さ、早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you, okay?{NOTE:お母さんも一緒に来ますから。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to go that much, then go without me.{NOTE:そんなに行きたきゃ、お母さん一人で行けば良いじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going there.{NOTE:あたしはいやよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!{NOTE:お待ちに…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!{NOTE:ゆり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you think you'll be able to persuade them?{NOTE:で、君には説得する自身があるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. To be honest, I'm not really sure.{NOTE:んん。それで実は困ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe you can think of something?{NOTE:ね、何か良い考えないかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that in the heat of the moment yesterday…{NOTE:昨日は弾みであんなこと言っちゃったけど、}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,…but I honestly don't think I can make friends with these girls.{NOTE:正直などこはあの人達と仲良くする何てできそうにないんもね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But both you and the Big Four share the love for volleyball, don't you.{NOTE:だけど、君達だって、四天王だって…バレーを愛することに軽いはないんだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do.{NOTE:それはもちろんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you join forces then?{NOTE:それだったらさ…なぜチームが組めれないんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think you've misunderstood each other.{NOTE:君達のどっかに誤解なるとしか考えられないね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world there are things that even bugs won't touch.{NOTE:世の中には虫が付かないってこともあるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.{NOTE:へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be harsh at times, you know.{NOTE:大体、君は頭にXXXだからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.{NOTE:ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered how you almost got in a fight with Hayakawa-san in the past.{NOTE:それに、早川くんの時だって、殴り合い寸前に成ったそうじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you knew it?{NOTE:あ、いやだ、知ってたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a newspaper club member for you.{NOTE:さすが新聞部は早耳ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you girls.{NOTE:あ、あなたたち…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.{NOTE:は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,– Sorry for all the trouble.\N– Eh?{NOTE:—色々お世話になりました。\\N—へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– We're quitting the volleyball club.\N– Oh, my.{NOTE:—あたしたちはバレー部を辞めるの。\\N—ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.{NOTE:ほら、この通り見てよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a resignation letter.\NWe're on the way to professor Hongou.{NOTE:退部届よ。今本郷先生に持ってく途中。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.{NOTE:そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls, haven't you staked everything on volleyball so far? And yet…{NOTE:あなたたち、バレーに命をかけていたじゃないの。それなのに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Staked everything"? Don't be absurd.{NOTE:命をかけた？ご冗談でしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a stupid ball game.{NOTE:あんなボール遊び何か…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not serious!{NOTE:嘘！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it more than you think.{NOTE:あたしには分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you're thinking that seriously.{NOTE:あなた方は嘘を付いてるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fool for volleyball too, so I get it.{NOTE:バレーバカに成ったあたしだから分かるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Training half for fun, unlike you, I can't get better.{NOTE:遊び半分の練習で、あなたたちほどの実力は付く分けないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?{NOTE:そうでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Fufufu. In other words, you're telling us we're geniuses?{NOTE:フフフ。その実力者を破ったXXXは、天才だとでも言いたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.{NOTE:さ、行きましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!{NOTE:待って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stubborn. Please?{NOTE:意地を張るのは止して。ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,– Please think it ove—\N– We've had enough.{NOTE:—よく考えて…\\N—XXXたくさんよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go.{NOTE:—行こう、行こう。\\N—行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to let them go like that?{NOTE:このままでしておいて良いのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!{NOTE:待って！待って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?{NOTE:な、何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—!{NOTE:な…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!{NOTE:何するのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give it back!{NOTE:—ちょっと返してよ！\\N—返してよ！待ちな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!{NOTE:返してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over here!{NOTE:早く返してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know Ayuhara-san can handle paperwork well.{NOTE:へ。鮎原くんは掻っ払いXXXしらなかったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Class 3C{NOTE:３年c組}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What a way to make a person look like a fool.{NOTE:まったく人をバカにしてやりかたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let her off the hook like that.{NOTE:このまま放っとくてはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't do something, I will.{NOTE:あんたたちやらなきゃ、あたしだけでもやる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I won't be staying silent.{NOTE:そうよ。黙ってられもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Katori-san. What about you?{NOTE:香取さん。あんたは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, same goes for me.{NOTE:そ…それは、あたしだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:よし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's notify someone.{NOTE:どっか呼び出そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the principal?{NOTE:富士見のXXからなんかどう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. {あたしはそう行ってくる。}I'll go.{NOTE:良いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's you.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing.{NOTE:ちょうどよかったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudou-san. I want to talk to you.{NOTE:工藤さん。あなたたちにちょっと話があるんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,– Talk?\N– Yep.{NOTE:—話？\\N—え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to see me by the riverbank after classes.{NOTE:授業が終わったら、富士見川のXXX来て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting. It's a promise!{NOTE:待ってるわ。きっとよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, she left me no choice.{NOTE:臭う、XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.{NOTE:XXX}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared for a company.{NOTE:どこにだれが隠れてるか知りやしないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awfully quiet.{NOTE:XXX静かね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people will be there?{NOTE:相手は何人来てるよ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can know it!{NOTE:そんなこと分かる分けないでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the others and focus on Ayuhara.{NOTE:他の人は良いから、鮎原だけをマークして。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?{NOTE:良いわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.{NOTE:いらっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.{NOTE:遅かったわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?{NOTE:あんた、一人？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Why are you asking?{NOTE:そうよ。なぜ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why have you called us here?{NOTE:じゃ、どうしたあたしたちを呼び出したのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I wanted to ask you.{NOTE:聞きたいことがあっただから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about this.{NOTE:これよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it.{NOTE:な、何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear whatever it is.{NOTE:言ってごらんなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to quit the volleyball club?{NOTE:あなたたちは本当にバレー部を辞めるつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do. Isn't that obvious?{NOTE:ん。もちろんよ。当たり前じゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have fought with you until now.{NOTE:あたしはあなたたちと争ってだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have always respected your talent.{NOTE:でもあなたたちの力を尊敬していたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect your serve and spike too, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あたくしだも鮎原さんのサーブとスパイクを尊敬しておりますのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?{NOTE:でしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If me and you join our forces, we might make an excellent team together.{NOTE:そのあたしとあなたたちは力を合わせたら、すごいチームに成ると思うけどな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious about that?{NOTE:本気でそう思ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.{NOTE:もちろん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same club and I want to win matches.{NOTE:だって、同じバレーをやりからには、試合に勝ちたいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to make a strong team even a little bit?{NOTE:少しでも…少しでも強いチームを作りたいでしょう?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same club?{NOTE:同じバレーをやるからには？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.{NOTE:お生憎様。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to see a volleyball ever again.{NOTE:あたしたち…二度とバレーボールを見るXXいやよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're dropping out no matter what?{NOTE:じゃ、どうしても退部届よ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the letters.{NOTE:返してよ、退部届。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you disturb us, I'm quitting.{NOTE:あんたはいくらじゃましたって、あたしたちは辞めるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with volleyball.{NOTE:バレーボールなんか糞XXXだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!{NOTE:返してよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.{NOTE:—返して。\\N—返して。\\N—返して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!{NOTE:—返すのよ。\\N—返すのよ。\\N—返すのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing!{NOTE:な、何すんのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah…{NOTE:あ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hate volleyball that much, let's see you cut up that ball.{NOTE:そんなにバレーが憎いなら、こうしてボールを裂いてごらんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see you tear that ball you don't want to see ever again.{NOTE:見にのもういやなボールならずだずだにしてごらんなさいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can do it, I'll give it up and give you the letters back.{NOTE:それができたら、あたしは諦めて退部届きを返しするわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.{NOTE:フン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.02,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Who needs volleyball.{NOTE:バレーが何よ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.90,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Who needs volleyball!{NOTE:バレーが何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.62,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Such a thing…{NOTE:こんなもの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:10.02,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Who needs that thing…{NOTE:何よ…こんなもの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.73,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Who needs it!{NOTE:バレーが何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:35.44,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Who needs this ball!{NOTE:ボールが何よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball is crying.{NOTE:ボールが泣くわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crying.{NOTE:泣いてるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Until yesterday, that ball was your true friend.{NOTE:ボールは昨日まであなたの親友だったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're trying to cut that friend to pieces!{NOTE:あなたはその親友をXXXとしている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!{NOTE:煩い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!{NOTE:辞めて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!{NOTE:危ない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…{NOTE:フン…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I…{NOTE:あたしには…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.{NOTE:あたしにはできないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we promise after entering Hamaki?{NOTE:浜紀中学に入る時に誓ったじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudou-san, Ozawa-san… we promised we'll continue with volleyball till high school…{NOTE:小沢さんも…小沢さんも。大学へ進んでまで必ずバレーボールを続けるって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{}Sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like Katori-san says.{NOTE:香取さんの言うとおりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't quit volleyball.{NOTE:あなたたちはバレーを辞めちゃいけないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your love for volleyball is true…{NOTE:XXバレーを愛してるのが本当なら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we even fight?{NOTE:なぜあたしたちはいがみ合ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't we united?{NOTE:なぜ手を合おってしないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozawa-san. Kudou-san, Katori-san…{NOTE:小沢さん。それから、工藤さん、香取さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!{NOTE:お願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.84,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make a team with us.{NOTE:あたしたちと一緒にチームを組んで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of that friendship.{NOTE:あの親友のために。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. One more time.{NOTE:あらちょっと。もう一つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:おい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!{NOTE:ほら頑張って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange.{NOTE:可笑しいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what chief's doing.{NOTE:親分、どうしたんだろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's take a break.{NOTE:よし、XXXにしましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san intends to get the Big Four back.{NOTE:鮎原さんね、四天王を連れってくるつもりなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so.{NOTE:あそうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't they come to us bowing their heads by now?{NOTE:でもさ、今さらあんな連中にペコペコすることないじゃん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be this simple.\NThey have their pride, you know.{NOTE:XXX人たちでもないし、ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.{NOTE:遅くに成りました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey.\N– Wow.{NOTE:—あら。\\N—まあ！。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{NOTE:わあ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she goes again.{NOTE:参った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got something to say, don't you?{NOTE:何が言いたいんだろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?{NOTE:で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,From the start we were thinking too much.{NOTE:もともと、あたしたちが考えすぎたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When we came here,\Nwe thought we'd be marginalized.{NOTE:ここに来たら、どうせXXXされるんだからって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To avoid it, we decided to seize the initiative first.{NOTE:それなら、先に主導権に握ってやろうって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we were thinking.{NOTE:そう思ったです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you were a little nervous just like us.{NOTE:つまり、あたしたちようかほんの少し神経質だったのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been rude to you.{NOTE:失礼なこと言っちゃって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.{NOTE:へへへへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it. We're over that.{NOTE:何。分かれば良いんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you, sports-girl. March with pride.{NOTE:スポーツマン、どうした。XXX行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Izumi though?{NOTE:では、泉はどうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,– Ah, she…\N– Well that's…{NOTE:—は…\\N—あの、それは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's absent from school today.{NOTE:今日は学校の休んだらしいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're worried about her as well.{NOTE:あたしたちも気にしているんですけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been acting strange since a few days ago.{NOTE:泉さんはこの二三日要すは可笑しかったから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?{NOTE:要すが？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, it feels like she was hiding something.{NOTE:そう言えば、何か隠したりみたいだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're great friends. It must be for a reason.{NOTE:だって、あなたたちは大の仲良しなんでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's surprisingly secretive though.{NOTE:それはさ…意外と秘密主義なのよう、彼女。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't blame her. Izumi-san's mom is actually her stepmother after all.{NOTE:無理ないわよ。泉さんの母さんて継母だから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A stepmother…{NOTE:継母…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tell her later. I'm sure she'll understand.{NOTE:後で行きます。きっと泉さんも分かってくれるわよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it goes well. She can be scary at times.{NOTE:うまく行くかな？彼女(XXX・無意義何と怖さら)ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Izumi-san, the name of Big Four loses its sense.{NOTE:泉くんはいないと、四天王の意味はなくなるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:その通りだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.75,0:22:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor. I'll go check on her and visit her home.{NOTE:先生。泉さんの家にあたしは行ってみます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.33,0:22:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, professor?{NOTE:ね、先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Let us go too then.{NOTE:あら、じゃ、あたしたちも一緒に行きましょうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You should focus on practice.{NOTE:あなたたちは練習、練習。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine by myself.{NOTE:あたし一人で大丈夫よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Let's leave it to Ayuhara.{NOTE:よし。じゃ、鮎原に行ってもらおう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.13,Sign,,0,0,0,,Izumi family{NOTE:泉}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mansion.{NOTE:大したお屋敷ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{NOTE:ごめんください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{NOTE:ごめんください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're out.{NOTE:お留守かしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.85,0:22:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?{NOTE:どなた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I beg your pardon, is Izumi Yuri-san home?{NOTE:あ、あの…泉ゆりさんいらっしゃいます？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're Yuri's friend?{NOTE:あ、ゆりのお友達？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am. My name's Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:はい。鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, nice to meet you. Welcome.{NOTE:あ、そうですか。どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri will be home soon. Make yourself comfortable.{NOTE:ゆりもう直ぐXXX。どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.90,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:22:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,However…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a member of the volleyball club, are you?{NOTE:あなた、バレー部の方じゃありませんわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Spot on. I am its member.{NOTE:当たりました。そのバレー部なんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid I can't let you meet with Yuri.{NOTE:バレー部の方にはいただけないんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for troubling you with this request only now, but could you please go home?{NOTE:わざわざで来ましたも悪いんですけど、このまま帰っていただきません？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, why is that? I came here out of the blue, but I'd rather not go home until I meet with Yuri.{NOTE:あ、なぜですか？あたし薮から棒にそんなこと言われても、あたし帰るわけにはいきません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:なぜですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.64,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and go home.{NOTE:黙って帰って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Izumi-san.{NOTE:あ、泉さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.{NOTE:ゆり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.{NOTE:帰ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.78,0:23:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not welcome here.{NOTE:ここはあんたのXXX所じゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.{NOTE:早く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!{NOTE:帰ってたら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:42.69,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:なぜ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.12,Alternative,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{NOTE:一体なぜなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.61,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kozue went alone to Izumi's home, but…{NOTE:こずえは一人泉の家を訪ねたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.61,0:24:00.04,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…when it became evident she's with\hthe volleyball\hclub, Izumi's stepmother coldens.{NOTE:バレー部の人間と分かったXX、泉の母の態度はXXXした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:04.59,Alternative,,0,0,0,,After Izumi Yuri gets home, she grabs Kozue's arm and drags her out…{NOTE:そこへ帰り合わせた泉ゆりはこずえの腕を掴んで、外へ追い立て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:07.95,Alternative,,0,0,0,,…shouting bitter words to her stepmother.{NOTE:母に大しても激しい言葉をXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:12.67,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Kozue can't shake off the feeling that there's something deeper going on.{NOTE:こずえは泉親と何か深いわけがあるに違いないと思ったのだが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:16.86,Alternative,,0,0,0,,But seeing Yuri's attitude, her hand reacts instinctively.{NOTE:こんな態度に、こずえは思わずゆりの方に手は飛んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:20.43,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
